reviewText: I wish I could give this a better rating but on the second session the filming is so dark in places; you can't see what she's doing.  For me personally; the instructors voice was irritating, not soothing.

My name is Angela. I just want to say that I love this dvd, It gives you 2 30 minute routines. Today I did the 1st. one and I have to say that she does not waste a minute of the routine, you work hard the whole body, strenght, flexibility and your going to swaet to. It is not repetitive, It changes all the time, so it work on your mind, you have to pay attention, I'll buy all the dvds. Try thid dvd. I'll say it is for beginners and intermediates, I'm an intermed. and I had so much fun with it. she tells you how to modified if you are a beginner. I love it!!!!!!!
